	"## Prompt Behavior\n" +
	"\n" +
	"The CLI automatically suppresses interactive prompts in non-interactive environments.\n" +
	"\n" +
	"### Prompt Suppression Rules\n" +
	"- Agent mode: All prompts suppressed (uses safe default: no)\n" +
	"- Human mode: Prompts allowed for interactive use\n" +
	"- --force flag: Bypasses all confirmation prompts (returns yes)\n" +
	"- --quiet flag: Suppresses prompts with safe default (no)\n" +
	"\n" +
	"### Flag-Based Alternatives\n" +
	"All operations that would prompt in human mode can be completed via flags:\n" +
